Allison Transmission



















Home/ Transmissions






Transmissions For more than 100 years, Allison Transmission has continuously discovered new ways to make work easier and more efficient. Believing our customers simply deserve the best, we design and build fully automatic transmissions that deliver premium performance with unrivaled reliability and durability.   Because of our commitment to quality, Allison is the world’s largest manufacturer of fully automatic transmissions and hybrid propulsion systems for commercial-duty vehicles.    Our transmissions can be found at work in cities and rural areas all around the world in a wide variety of applications. From refuse and distribution to mining and school buses – if the job needs to get done, customers count on Allison.    To learn more about the superior features and benefits of Allison fully automatic transmissions (“Allison Automatics”), check out our many vocational applications and models – including our defense product line and hybrid technology products. Or if you’re ready to personally experience the smooth, uninterrupted shifting of Allison transmissions and want to find out more about how we can help increase your productivity, contact a local Allison representative today.










Vocational Applications
Hybrid
Models
Back to Top






Vocational Applications Allison Transmission introduced the world’s first fully automatic transmission for commercial vehicles nearly 70 years ago. Since that time, we have developed a global reputation as the leading manufacturer of high quality, reliable, medium- and heavy-duty automatic transmissions. Our success and global reach is driven by Allison’s commitment to providing the best transmission technology for your business. Rather than offer a few standard transmission options, we’ve created a series of transmissions that provide features and technology designed to deliver exceptional performance and efficiency in a variety of commercial vehicle applications. From the rugged terrain of an active construction site to the busy streets and highways of a city, Allison transmissions (“Allison Automatics”) are designed and built specifically to deliver superior results, even in the most challenging work conditions.   Find your application and explore how an Allison Automatic can bring extraordinary value to your company. 












