Allison Transmission Holdings Inc.


            
            Allison Transmission Holdings, Inc. engages in the designing and manufacturing of transmissions for commercial and tactical vehicles, as well as hybrid-propulsion systems for transit buses, through its subsidiaries. It operates through a single segment, Manufacture and Distribution of Fully-Automatic Transmissions. The company was founded on June 22, 2007 and is headquartered in Indianapolis, IN.

            
